er in the wedding ceremony.", "words": [{"w": "The", "s": 24.06, "e": 24.62}, {"w": "couple", "s": 24.62, "e": 24.88}, {"w": "made", "s": 24.88, "e": 25.18}, {"w": "a", "s": 25.18, "e": 25.26}, {"w": "commitment", "s": 25.26, "e": 25.64}, {"w": "to", "s": 25.64, "e": 26.0}, {"w": "each", "s": 26.0, "e": 26.2}, {"w": "other", "s": 26.2, "e": 26.48}, {"w": "in", "s": 26.48, "e": 26.78}, {"w": "the", "s": 26.78, "e": 26.94}, {"w": "wedding", "s": 26.94, "e": 27.14}, {"w": "ceremony.", "s": 27.14, "e": 27.86}]}, {"start": 30.56, "end": 33.88, "text": "I studied English literature at college.", "words": [{"w": "I", "s": 30.56, "e": 31.46}, {"w": "studied", "s": 31.46, "e": 31.86}, {"w": "English", "s": 31.86, "e": 32.26}, {"w": "literature", "s": 32.26, "e": 32.9}, {"w": "at", "s": 32.9, "e": 33.3}, {"w": "college.", "s": 33.3, "e": 33.88}]}, {"start": 36.6, "end": 40.38, "text": "This charity provides support to the local community.", "words": [{"w": "This", "s": 36.6, "e": 37.5}, {"w": "charity", "s": 37.5, "e": 37.9}, {"w": "provides", "s": 37.9, "e": 38.4}, {"w": "support", "s": 38.4, "e": 38.98}, {"w": "to", "s": 38.98, "e": 39.24}, {"w": "the", "s": 39.24, "e": 39.36}, {"w": "local", "s": 39.36, "e": 39.64}, {"w": "community.", "s": 39.64, "e": 40.38}]}, {"start": 43.06, "end": 47.36, "text": "A number of activists protested outside the government building.", "words": [{"w": "A", "s": 43.06, "e": 43.86}, {"w": "number", "s": 43.86, "e": 44.1}, {"w": "of", "s": 44.1, "e": 44.28}, {"w": "activists", "s": 44.28, "e": 44.88}, {"w": "protested", "s": 44.88, "e": 45.8}, {"w": "outside", "s": 45.8, "e": 46.1}, {"w": "the", "s": 46.1, "e": 46.48}, {"w": "government", "s": 46.48, "e": 46.82}, {"w": "building.", "s": 46.82, "e": 47.36}]}, {"start": 50.26, "end": 54.04, "text": "Students at this school are very active and volunteering.", "words": [{"w": "Students", "s": 50.26, "e": 51.16}, {"w": "at", "s": 51.16, "e": 51.54}, {"w": "this", "s": 51.54, "e": 51.74}, {"w": "scho